<p>You may think this is a funny piece of advice for me to write on my blog.</p>
<p>But if you care about earning more as a freelance writer, then you might want to stop writing blog posts.</p>
<p>Why do I say this?</p>
<p>There are four big reasons I want to steer you away from blogging:</p>
