		<description><![CDATA[<p><img align="right" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-4065" src="http://www.makealivingwriting.com/wp-content/uploads/photodune-437376-businessman-signing-a-contract-xs-e1415994550644-199x300.jpg" alt="Freelance writer signs contract" width="199" height="300" /></p>
<p>Eight years is a long time to not know what you’re doing as a freelance writer.</p>
<p>But that’s exactly how long it took me to figure out how to get serious and treat my freelance career as a business.</p>
<p>I hope my story helps you figure it out a lot faster than that.</p>
